<div class="container py-5 col lh-base">
    <h1 class="mt-5">API Docs</h1>
    <p class="h5 mt-2 lead"><em> The Author API is a free REST API for retrieving images of book authors </em></p>
    <h3 class="mt-5">Example REQUEST</h3>

    <section class="">
        <ul class="lh-lg">
            <li>METHOD: <b> GET</b></li>
            <li> URL: <a href="https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors?fn=Cormac">https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors?fn=Cormac</a>  </li>
            <li>Result</li>
        </ul>
        <pre class="block">
            <code class="language-js">
                {
                    _id: new ObjectId("6392342563fca3e188faedd4"),
                    firstName: 'Cormac',
                    lastName: 'McCarthy',
                    born: 1933-07-20T00:00:00.000Z,
                    __v: 0
                  }
              
            </code>
          </pre>
          <p class="fs-5"> <em> Every Author has a unique ID number which can be used to retieve all of the images associated with that author via the /api/authors/:id route </em></p>
          <ul class="lh-lg">
            <li>METHOD: GET</li>
            <li>URL: <a href="https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors/6392342563fca3e188faedd4">https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors/6392342563fca3e188faedd4 </a></li>
            <li>Result:
            </li>
            <pre class="block">
                <code class="language-js">
                    [{"url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dl3kwv1jr/image/upload/v1670526012/authors/yhwqpejytdzwo9d1jryh.jpg"}]
                  
                </code>
              </pre>
          </ul>
          <h3>Query Params</h3>
          <p class="h5">The API supports two query parameters at the moment</p>
          <table class="table table-striped table-dark">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">#</th>
                <th scope="col">Parameter</th>
                <th scope="col">Example URL</th>
                <th scope="col">Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row">1</th>
                <td>fn</td>
                <td><a href="https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors?fn=Cormac">https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors?fn=Cormac</a></td>
                <td>First name of the author</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th scope="row">2</th>
                <td>ln</td>
                <td><a href="https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors?ln=McCarthy">https://authorapi.up.railway.app/api/authors?ln=McCarthy</a></td>
                <td>Last name of the author</td>
              </tr>
              
            </tbody>
          </table>
    </section>
